slots.description: Change the item to display when there are no items in the table.

attributes.name: v-model / model-value
attributes.description: binding time value

attributes.name: v-model
attributes.description: Determination if the component is active (visible).

attributes.name: color
attributes.description: color of the tooltip.

attributes.name: left, right, bottom
attributes.description: position of the tooltip.

attributes.name: border
attributes.description: Change the style of the tooltip by adding a border.

attributes.name: border-thick
attributes.description: Change the style of the tooltip by adding a thick border only at the arrow position.

attributes.name: square
attributes.description: Determine if the tooltip is rectangular without border-radius.

attributes.name: circle
attributes.description: Change the border radius to 20px so that if it is a single line of text the corners are circular.

attributes.name: shadow
attributes.description: Change the style of the tooltip by adding a shadow and changing the background.

attributes.name: not-arrow
attributes.description: Remove the arrow from the tooltip.

attributes.name: not-hover
attributes.description: The default tooltip is generated by doing hover on the parent element, that functionality is removed and no longer appears or disappears when doing hover.

attributes.name: interactivity
attributes.description: Determine if the tooltip is interactive and makes it possible to click without automatically hiding.

attributes.name: loading
attributes.description: Determine if the tooltip has a loading style and animation.

attributes.name: default
attributes.description: Add the trigger element of the tooltip.

attributes.name: content
attributes.description: It is the content that will go inside the tooltip.
